    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Councilor Mairra Voss — The Sympathetic Councilor</h2>\n<p><em>Late fifties. Formerly a trade-clearing notary in Loftwick; now a sitting councilor. Voted against the Closure motion; lost 4–3. Will support a renewed vote if the party brings her a clean documentary case. Notary first, councilor second.</em></p>\n<h3>Combat behavior</h3>\n<p><strong>None.</strong> Yields.</p>\n<h3>Statblock summary (CR 0, PB +2)</h3>\n<p>AC 11 · HP 22 (5d8) · Speed 30 ft. · Init +0 · Passive Perception 14</p>\n<p>STR 10 · DEX 11 · CON 11 · INT 16 · WIS 16 · CHA 14. Saves: INT +5. Skills: History +5, Insight +5, Investigation +5, Perception +5, Persuasion +4.</p>\n<h3>Source</h3>\n<p><em>Blooming Rot, Part 2 — Phase 5.</em> See <em>Phase 5 — Loftwick NPCs → Mairra Voss — The Sympathetic Councilor</em> for the four documentary cases she will accept.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
